
 Steps to building and testing the entity extraction rules

 You need access to the reuter corpus to run these scripts.

 1. Extract training data from articles with extract_txt.pl

 2. Verify a_train.txt and r_train.txt

 3. Run bld_ruleent.pl to create the co_ruleent.txt file

 4. Load the co_ruleent.txt file into the co_ruleent DB table

 Files			Description
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 a_train.txt		Additional training text
 bld_ruleent.pl		Build the entity extraction rules
 co_ruleent.txt		Entity extraction rules
 doc.txt		Output file after running extract_doc.pl
 extract_doc.pl		Extract articles from the Reuters collection for
                        a set of categories
 extract_txt.pl		Extract training data from the Reuters articles
 r_train.txt		Output file after running extract_txt.pl
